The People of the State of Illinois, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. Zygmund Nogas, Defendant-Appellant.(No. 59013;First District (3rd Division)March 7, 1974.

DEMPSEY, J., took no part.

PER CURIAM. James J. Doherty, Public Defender, of Chicago (Suzanne M. Xinos, Assistant Public Defender, of counsel), for appellant. Bernard Carey, State’s Attorney, of Chicago (Kenneth L. Gillis and Barry Rand Elden, Assistant State’s Attorneys, of counsel), for the People.
